# LIMKTG101
# LI Marketing 101

How to create a LinkedIn .QR Code

Step 1) go to LinkedIn app.
Step 2) Click on the 🔍 Search Bar
Step 3) Go to blinking “|”
Step 4) Click My Code > Share my code > Share with Photo > Copy + Paste
Step 4) Open any Email Application (Desktop or Phone ✅) Go To: New Message/Compose.
Step 5) Paste Code into Body of Message.
Step 6) Press Send.

Done.
